## Quick Example

![Demo](demo.gif)

Transform messy filenames into clean, organized ones:

```
Before:                               After:
üìÑ paper_final_v3.pdf          ‚Üí     Leroux-Analog-In-memory-Computing-2025.pdf
üìÑ download (2).pdf            ‚Üí     Ruiz-Why-Don-Trace-Requirements-2023.pdf
üìÑ document.pdf                ‚Üí     Raspail-Camp_of_the_Saints.pdf
```

